<Base title="SocialProof for Wedding Planners — Testimonials That Fill Your Booking Calendar | SocialProof" description="Wedding planners: capture authentic couple testimonials and display them on your website. SocialProof helps you turn every dream wedding into the social proof that books your next one.">
  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for Wedding Planners
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Couples searching for a wedding planner are making one of the biggest emotional purchases of their lives. Before they schedule a discovery call, they spend hours reading everything they can find about you. Your Instagram is beautiful — but your testimonials are what make them pick up the phone. SocialProof helps you collect and display those testimonials automatically, so your website closes couples before you ever speak.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">The testimonial is your most powerful sales tool</h2>
      <p>Portfolio photos show what you produce. Testimonials reveal who you are to work with — how you kept calm when the venue double-booked, how you made the bride's mom feel included, how you magically turned a rainy outdoor ceremony into something memorable. That's what separates you from every other planner with a beautiful website.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">SocialProof gives you a simple widget that displays those stories right on your site — with zero technical setup and automatic updates as new testimonials come in.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">What couples write when you've made their day perfect</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>The day itself:</strong> "I didn't think about a single logistical thing on my wedding day. I was completely present. That's because of her."</li>
        <li><strong>Vendor magic:</strong> "Found us a florist in four days when ours had a family emergency. Better flowers than the original. Unbelievable."</li>
        <li><strong>Emotional intelligence:</strong> "Navigated two very different families with total grace. Both sides felt heard. That's not easy."</li>
        <li><strong>Budget stewardship:</strong> "Helped us get our dream wedding at a budget we actually felt good about. Every dollar was thoughtful."</li>
        <li><strong>Communication:</strong> "Always reachable, always calm, always two steps ahead. Made planning feel like a joy, not a stress."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How SocialProof works for your wedding business</h2>
      <ol style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Embed the widget</strong> on your website — takes under 10 minutes, no developer needed.</li>
        <li><strong>Send the collection link</strong> 1–2 weeks after the wedding, when the couple is back from honeymoon and glowing.</li>
        <li><strong>Approve and publish</strong> each testimonial with one click from your dashboard.</li>
        <li><strong>Build your library</strong> — every wedding adds to the proof that closes your next booking.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">The post-honeymoon window</h2>
      <p>The perfect moment to ask for a wedding testimonial is when the couple returns from their honeymoon — they're tan, relaxed, and still riding the high. A personal text from you: "Welcome back! We loved being part of your day. If you have a few minutes, a quick note about working together would mean the world: [link]." Response rates at this moment are consistently over 60%. Don't miss it.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Works for every wedding planning service</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li>Full-service wedding planning</li>
        <li>Partial planning and month-of coordination</li>
        <li>Day-of coordination</li>
        <li>Elopements and micro-weddings</li>
        <li>Destination weddings</li>
        <li>LGBTQ+ weddings</li>
        <li>Cultural and multi-tradition ceremonies</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Start free — no credit card required</h2>
      <p>SocialProof is free forever for one active widget. Start collecting from your last few couples and see how quickly your inquiry rate climbs.</p>
